  <name>Tarot Canvas</name>
  <summary>Cross-platform Qt application for viewing and exploring tarot decks</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Tarot Canvas is a cross-platform application for viewing and exploring tarot decks.
      It adheres to the Tarot Deck Specification v1.0 to ensure compatibility across
      different decks and platforms.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Load and view tarot decks that follow the Tarot Deck Specification</li>
      <li>Support for multiple card formats including SVG and raster images</li>
      <li>Internationalization support</li>
      <li>Custom card backs and variants</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
